    <ul class="outline-list">
      <li>Keystone + durable boundary + Attempt + three budgets + park/grant + Target checkpoint</li>
      <li>#ledger: Session task ledger ≠ TaskRun (identity / evidence / tools)</li>
      <li>Three continuations (Harbor Turn / Autonomous Attempt / parked CLI) kept semantically distinct</li>
      <li>#harbor-trust isolation assertion + #swarm / Expert Team (≠ TaskRun)</li>
